      "content": "hey, im working on a new streetwear line and i want to make sure it feels authentic to the street without it looking like just another brand trying to cash in on urban culture. can u help me define the core aesthetic of 'urban culture' so i can stay respectful? like, what are the visual hallmarks i should look into?",
