      "content": "thanks, that's a good start. u mentioned hip-hop and the \"struggles\" part. when u say the aesthetic should reflect those struggles, are there specific groups or demographics i should be looking at more closely to make sure the vibe is right? like, is there a certain look that's more \"authentic\" to those specific communities?",
